# Elly Conventions (Skill: elly-conventions)

Kanonik kaynak: `.claude/skills/elly-conventions/SKILL.md`

## Paket Yapisi
```
com.cms.
├── config/          # Spring konfigurasyonlari
├── controller/      # IXxxController interface
│   └── impl/        # XxxController implementasyonlari
├── service/         # IXxxService interface
│   └── impl/        # XxxService implementasyonlari
├── repository/      # Spring Data JPA
├── entity/          # JPA @Entity
├── mapper/          # MapStruct @Mapper
├── dto/request/     # CreateRequest, UpdateRequest
├── dto/response/    # XxxResponse
├── exception/       # BaseException alt siniflari
└── enums/           # Enum tanimlari
```

## Zorunlu Pattern
```java
// Entity: @Data @Builder @NoArgsConstructor @AllArgsConstructor @Entity @Table
// Service: @Service @RequiredArgsConstructor @Transactional
// Controller: @RestController @RequiredArgsConstructor
// Mapper: @Mapper(componentModel = "spring")
// Response: RootEntityResponse<T> ile wrap
// DI: Constructor injection (@RequiredArgsConstructor), ASLA @Autowired field
```

## Yasak Pratikler
- Entity'yi dogrudan controller'dan dondurme → MapStruct kullan
- `@Autowired` field injection → `@RequiredArgsConstructor`
- Tenant context olmadan cross-tenant query
- Controller icinde `@Transactional`
- Cache key'lerinde tenantId'yi elle ekleme (otomatik)
